{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2017}} {{Use British English|date=January 2017}} '''Lizanne Henderson''' is a Senior Lecturer in history at the [[University of Glasgow]] in [[Crichton Campus|Dumfries]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gla.ac.uk/departments/dumfriescampus/newsandevents/headline_81611_en.html|title=Dr Lizanne Henderson on German visit|publisher=University of Glasgow |date=18 June 2008 |accessdate=26 February 2011}}</ref>{{dead link|date=January 2018}}
