ew York. * Coe, Michael D. (2006) Final Report: An Archaeologist Excavates His Past. Thames and Hudson, New York. * Coe, Michael D. (2006) The Line of Forts: Historical Archaeology on the Colonial Frontier of Massachusetts. University Press of New England, Lebanon.
